{"tid":792041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"___ 係一個比南亞人強姦的女仔（2）","createTime":"2018-08-24T09:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T11:30:48.000Z","uid":128210,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5795a5a5a24072fe2d3c2bc2ce299f8b110918e6","tid":792041,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"我係一個比南亞人強姦嘅女仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/791626?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/791626?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/172212_c16121cec47b3c6bb84e812ac9a61dc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F172212_c16121cec47b3c6bb84e812ac9a61dc5.jpg&h=11445a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係唔係suki ???<br />\n做咩以前咁健談，而家成日潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾機會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係全ive最弱智o個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541a79cf7e20bc0157a541467a135ca52138d478","tid":792041,"uid":71238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d95145d514ae3ca90a59ce2f8457a9091908e1ef","tid":792041,"uid":71238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe5ff73f30b2a893f95505c35d712e7c28e0f45","tid":792041,"uid":71238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c2d7b781353c4464f573da47992992a9e897f5","tid":792041,"uid":71238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b85d29259957c2c75dd7ae6038efd6e3ab71a80","tid":792041,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rainlily.org.hk/rainlily.php?p=ineedhelp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rainlily.org.hk%2Frainlily.php%3Fp%3Dineedhelp&d=itMRmcMEBhBK6NMbRZTM%2BP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=52f82f1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rainlily.org.hk/rainlily.php?p=ineedhelp</a><br />\n<br />\n全港首間性暴力危機中心「風雨蘭」成立於2000年。免費提供包括即時輔導、法醫檢查、錄取口供、提供事後避孕、性病檢查及預防治療、法律資訊等適切支援，以協助全港遭受性暴力的女性重建自尊自信。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n風雨蘭在九龍及新界設有一站式危機中心，結合各服務及相關程序與中心內進行，避免幸存者周旋於不同部門之間，重複講述被害經驗，加深創傷。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n危機中心所提供的二十四小時一站式服務，可以減低受害人因揭露性侵犯事件而再度受創的機會，並每年為超過二百位受害女性及其家人提供可靠的服務。<br />\n<br />\n雖然樓主係on9 仔 但都希望事主睇到<br />\n可以唔話比朋友 屋企人知都有人幫架"},{"pid":"01481c642a6f41b3ea0071baddd91f1999458ace","tid":792041,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"弱智，真係比人姦就唔會講一大段野話自己好好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c697a67c00c092723d7cf9a5ba5762313b80e22","tid":792041,"uid":25973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"01481c642a6f41b3ea0071baddd91f1999458ace","tid":792041,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"弱智，真係比人姦就唔會講一大段野話自己好好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"你知香港幾多人中意屈人係壞女人先會比人強姦架啦 想講明自己唔係d先都幾正常姐"},{"pid":"da73a461172f1ccd0dd73270e4ade9db09478063","tid":792041,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"好想事主入黎答我係唔係suki 。<br />\n<br />\n我識的suki 又係女校，又係會同男仔保持距離。<br />\n一直同佢男友拍拖。<br />\n但